* Environment\nIsolation Strategy
** Separate catalogs per environment
***_ sales_dev, sales_test, sales_prod
***_ Permissions at catalog level
** Combine domain + environment
***_ Pattern: {domain}_{environment}
***_ Scales across business domains
** Organize by layer within environment
***_ sales_bronze, sales_silver, sales_gold
***_ prod catalog for all production data
** External sharing
***_ customer_analytics_shared
***_ Avoid internal naming exposure
** Storage paths mirror conventions
***_ env/layer/domain/table/
@endmindmap
